Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自地面永恆的希望\N(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.19,0:01:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏，魯烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.66,0:01:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還是休息比較好吧，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.75,0:01:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.17,0:01:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個宇宙會有沒有戰火的一天嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.97,0:01:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要陛下希望的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕希望!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.28,0:02:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾巴號一直固定發出\N要遞結和平協定的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那不是透過正式管道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單方面說要締結和平協定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.86,0:02:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕幕僚高官們\N是不會相信的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連妳自己都不信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那個訊息是否正式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那畢竟是梅爾巴發出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個權限的人\N只有少數幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.81,0:02:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是旺克宰相\N就是羅那瓦提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是阿薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿薩琳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.95,0:02:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個人一定是想\N傳達真正的事實吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標準時間1205
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸船、護衛艦蜻蛉號\N及其他三艘艦艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在邊境空域受到襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損害狀況、生存者等等\N詳細情形正在調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蛉號是山本上尉坐的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.02,0:03:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再重覆一遍，標準時間1205\N運輸船、護衛艦蜻蛉號及其他三艘艦艇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊境空域的襲擊是何人所為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.44,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,締結和平協定是否是拉爾哥方面的真意\N目前一切都無法斷定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.36,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，目前拉爾哥艦隊在\N邊境空域至重兵集結是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍應該做出擊準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第七機動部隊\N已經在待命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是邊境方面軍的精銳部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過數目差敵人艦隊太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交戰狀態再持續下去的話\N沒人能保證一定撐得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.01,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子邊境麻煩大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是一艘運輸船的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一方面軍司令長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.07,0:04:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，你想說\N需要新型高速巡洋艦是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個意外事故，發生得真是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是意外事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.25,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以邊境空域為中心\N情勢開始在改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦隊要是突破防衛線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時別說是和平交涉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.09,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我軍的存續都有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊境已經不是邊境了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次說邊境方面軍已經\N做好執行R號計畫的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人\N已經抵達指示的地點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛師團的艦隊\N也各自到達預定的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，留在這裡待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.29,0:05:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，卡爾基蘭驅艦\N傳來通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人情況怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，偵察機回報說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.30,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人機動艦隊正以\N巡航速度向我方艦隊接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對應我方行動\N而採取的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.89,0:05:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，您還在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.06,0:05:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛師團調動出來\N梅爾巴無人防守那件事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.48,0:05:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有羅那瓦提督閣下在\N您應該不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是閉門思過中嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳正在調查事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事無論如何\N應該讓妳知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事故中\N有找到什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.72,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，自從這次也收到\N同樣訊號的報告後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該能查出很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼訊號之外的事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訊號之外?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊我們的是紅色的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，是紅色的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.12,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等那陣光芒包圍船隻之後\N所有儀器都失靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道光芒來自什麼方向嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑盒子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.29,0:06:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑盒子沒有記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過菲薩砲的雷達上\N應該有記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查部回收走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋茲中士\N請立刻跟調查部連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.89,0:06:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能知道紅色光芒是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想應該會\N透露出信號之外的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，山本上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這都是小暮上尉的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.75,0:07:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，梅爾巴那邊沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是強力的干擾電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干擾電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星聯合宇宙軍機動部隊\N快出現在我們前方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能用了新式的亞空間航法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取戰鬥隊形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在了解梅爾巴號狀況前\N繼續待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解，全艦隊採取戰鬥隊形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接上卡爾基蘭號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.24,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要與敵人艦隊決戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦的攻擊目標是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我們不出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾巴號的通訊中斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳立刻派偵察機去調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾巴訊息中斷!?\N了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，無法通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾巴號被異常電磁波包圍起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁波…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說是行星聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們連跟近衛師團通訊都沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特姆他們嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，再不吃點東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體會撐不住的\N至少吃一口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆有沒有傳來連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.04,0:08:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以特姆大人的能力\N您絕對不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕擔心的不只是特姆呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，他振作起來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到要再跟他見面\N我人就鬱卒，輸給他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天都喊著小暮小暮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他今天不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.56,0:09:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在調查\N他自己遭受襲擊的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.18,0:09:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紅色的光芒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.39,0:09:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的光芒不會是\N拉爾哥的新武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.94,0:09:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的96式已經完成\N可以跟他們火拼一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.57,0:09:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個\N96式是地上戰鬥用的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.53,0:09:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他地上還是宇宙\N戰鬥就是戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:09:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.29,0:10:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我是說新武器跟要求和平的通訊\N很難連貫起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是戰略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.55,0:10:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想為和平協定\N賺取有利的籌碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後要求和平的通訊\N中斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，太唐突了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.06,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是山本副艦長的船\N遭到攻擊是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.23,0:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到拉爾哥攻擊嗎\N你們不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，由理子妳的看法呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.07,0:10:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拉爾哥帝國的作風\N應該會拿新武器出來炫耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為和平交涉的籌碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在停止和平交涉\N時間好像不太對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要求和平的人\N跟襲擊的人是不同人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾哥內部分裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.47,0:10:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們分裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊有新武器\N另一邊沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種實力懸殊的勢力\N可能共存嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是我們的山本要調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回分析部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理子，今天的份是我墊付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒妳要付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，梅爾巴號的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.88,0:11:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現來歷不明的部隊\N正向帝國領土接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵察機只留下\N發現紅色光芒的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，紅色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.89,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.65,0:11:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的機動艦隊已\N超越我方艦隊的防衛網了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被敵人的聲東擊西戰術給騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.15,0:11:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星聯合宇宙軍沒有戰力\N展開這種大規模的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計得太巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.95,0:12:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人彷彿早就料到\N梅爾巴號沒有艦隊防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.54,0:12:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這更像是敵人\N故意引導我們離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.80,0:12:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個放肆的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果出來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士，你解釋給他聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，首先請看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那兩個訊號資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以異於軍方標準方式的各種方式解讀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.44,0:13:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的答案都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於帶磁流星群的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 可是…\N- 可是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.16,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以音響分析系統\N將訊息切換成聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個，那時候\N我也聽到這個聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，這個飛行雷達\N錄音下來的聲音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後更有趣的在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.30,0:13:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強這個訊號\N取出低到高周波的訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.86,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個訊號都重複著\N同一模式的的電磁波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不是帶磁流星群\N是人為製造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.70,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，這不是\N拉爾哥帝國的信號波型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你看一下這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是邊境空域的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.51,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，這是普通時候\N然後這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.43,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到襲擊時拍的\N攝影位置一樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有何不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，這是普通的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是被襲擊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有差別嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有，就是這裡\N這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是普通時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是受襲擊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受襲擊的時候\N星星消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我跟雷達觀測站詢問的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.55,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個位置的星星\N實際上並沒有消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說星星的光芒\N是被遮住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說因為角度的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恆星的光芒給遮住了\N可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個分析結果都顯示\N那是人工的電磁波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為遮住這位置的\N絕不是恆星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個需要電腦進一步分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我猜這裡就是\N紅色光芒的中心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.66,0:15:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子事情有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本上尉\N我不知道能多逼真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，形狀應該還看得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片的底片\N已經輸入進去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位好像沒什麼休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是\N增加你們工作量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉你也很辛苦呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是大發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒把分析用的電腦\N全部開動就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會花太多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.57,0:16:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.53,0:16:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析無別鑑別的訊號後發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.29,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人為製造的物體\N發出的電磁波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N襲擊我的護衛艦隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是帶磁流星群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是拉爾哥帝國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是另外的一批人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍還不知道敵人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部就派第三、第七機動部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去加強邊境的防衛線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.48,0:16:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果… 我軍跟拉爾哥軍\N都被人耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照此下去，不信任帶來的\N全面衝突是無法避免的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.95,0:16:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說軍方決定將\N新型高速巡洋艦派去邊境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R號計畫\N交給邊境方面軍了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.55,0:17:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情報再由情報局提報上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的想法我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是事實\N我軍得立刻想出對策才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.10,0:17:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你閣下\N請准許屬下出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.69,0:17:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了，你可以退下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的，交給我們軍司令部判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?閣下\N請讓我們去邊境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去邊境?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請准許微風號出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們出擊想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.83,0:17:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除誤會\N締結和平協定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.46,0:17:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平?你們相信那個通訊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.43,0:17:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船中將\N你還是明白告訴他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微風號已經註定要解體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，不必我說\N你們也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.07,0:18:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次三船中將是\N全艦隊的司令長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，搭乘的是\N新型高速巡洋艦肥前號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.91,0:18:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我忘記說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.45,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中將指名你當肥前號的艦長哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該感謝三船中將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你對邊境很了解\N所以才推薦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.38,0:18:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受悔過處份的人\N還能當上艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是多大恩惠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.42,0:18:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.07,0:18:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的微風號要被解體了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拆成廢鐵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說他們派我們到地上執勤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打這主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之大家安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是反對呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方在想什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理子前輩跟山本副艦長\N也是被矇在鼓裡的人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.51,0:19:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿酒來，拿酒來\N拿一整箱過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.18,0:19:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要大醉特醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.68,0:19:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒艦長\N我看你好像胸有成竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.65,0:19:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實問題不在於\N微風號被解體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的微風號要被解體了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意，大家湊過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，艦長!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.14,0:20:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平是虛妄，是敗北
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是被選上的子民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.15,0:20:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以不屈不撓的鬥志戰鬥下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.11,0:20:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的美酒\N等著我們共飲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.32,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全艦隊發下\N總攻擊的命令吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.42,0:20:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人\N發艦命令還沒發佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦載機就已經出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑，是誰命令的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.64,0:20:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，旗艦梅爾巴號\N發出總攻擊的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾巴號?能通訊了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是單方面的發訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.44,0:20:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要確認是誰發的消息\N梅爾巴號一概不接受訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.82,0:20:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，西雅哈絲\N盡量阻止我方行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個攻擊命令不是羅那瓦\N也不是陛下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.79,0:21:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.88,0:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旺克…旺克叛亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰相他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就立刻把艦隊調往梅爾巴號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人就在眼前\N我們無法撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.64,0:21:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西雅哈絲，盡量避開敵人攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保存實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.52,0:21:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被旺克給陷害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.83,0:21:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦載機\N即將進入戰鬥區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.42,0:21:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.48,0:21:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，發動全部艦載機\N迎擊敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，全體出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求和果然是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.36,0:22:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的艦載機出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定中的行動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想實在是脆弱呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.26,0:22:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於開戰了，中將大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.60,0:22:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平果然是不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.06,0:22:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人在偷偷摸摸幹什麼\N還想做無謂掙扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.44,0:22:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上山本上尉說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.82,0:23:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓海兵隊員加入肥前號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在想什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.74,0:23:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以為中將大人會答應嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.70,0:23:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群天真的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.83,0:23:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.33,0:23:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.92,0:23:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說他們對邊境很了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.84,0:23:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我沒理由拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.93,0:23:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，已經取得海兵隊員\N上肥前號的登船許可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，香取你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.27,0:23:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安裝上是沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.52,0:23:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就怕微風號的裝甲\N無法承受它的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.98,0:23:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.73,0:23:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.36,0:23:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春美，春美醒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.08,0:23:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.58,0:23:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平… 和平協定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.04,0:23:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍總司令官\N羅那瓦提督的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.80,0:24:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們帝國的民意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.09,0:24:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在已經無法與\N旗艦梅爾巴號通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.60,0:24:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們拉爾哥帝國的意願\N是不改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.56,0:24:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特羅梅號的訊息?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.90,0:24:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特姆艦長說的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.03,0:24:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆艦長也無法跟\N梅爾巴號通訊，這表示…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.45,0:24:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然梅爾巴號出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.87,0:24:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.12,0:24:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，我們應該趕快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.63,0:24:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了，夠了，羅那瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.75,0:24:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，微臣原想抵死戰鬥到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.47,0:24:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻力不從心，真是慚愧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅那瓦，朕知道你的忠心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.93,0:24:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕才要請你原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.48,0:24:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，您怎可這麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.77,0:25:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先帝駕崩後，你一直對年幼的朕忠心耿耿\N朕禮當向你道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.99,0:25:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.24,0:25:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕不知道士兵與民心所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.95,0:25:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會我行我素\N身為皇帝朕該感到羞恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.04,0:25:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該戰鬥的對手\N其實是朕的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.25,0:25:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕太自大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.38,0:25:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒朕，羅那瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.46,0:25:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下您長大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.64,0:25:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也沒有遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.68,0:25:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼\N戰鬥現在才開始呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.65,0:25:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.66,0:25:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人命令屬下來保護陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.49,0:25:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.62,0:25:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，請準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.37,0:26:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 朕知道了\N- 逃脫辦法呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.29,0:26:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經悄悄準備逃生用太空梭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.39,0:26:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，您看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.94,0:26:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，我先在太空等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.45,0:26:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.96,0:27:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時要告別地上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.88,0:27:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在那裡沒什麼好回憶\N還是有點寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.46,0:27:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，你連續遭女人拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.63,0:27:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.89,0:27:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.28,0:27:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連絡各艦艇，準備發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.45,0:27:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.82,0:27:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全體人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.28,0:28:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起向邊境空域33A地點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.58,0:28:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾哥帝國艦隊出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.79,0:28:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動前一分鐘\N開始倒數讀秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.42,0:28:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很樂的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:10.96,0:28:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，微風號的人\N這下子只有死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.89,0:28:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說他們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.14,0:28:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您擔心什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.26,0:28:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤中將，我們連敵人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.14,0:28:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平條約，一切事實都不明呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.48,0:28:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這什麼話，中將\N我們就要出發戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.49,0:28:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前敵人… 還是拉爾哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.03,0:28:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點點就可以\N查出敵人的身份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.33,0:28:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.25,0:28:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.54,0:28:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個螢幕可能會撐不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.38,0:28:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄的殘留電磁波太強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.05,0:28:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換到主螢幕上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.39,0:28:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.41,0:29:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥前號，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.06,0:29:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長，敵人船艦在五點鐘方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.90,0:29:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，重整隊形然後攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:03.45,0:30:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防衛線33A地點被突破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.87,0:30:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦首受損嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.66,0:30:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，請下令應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.17,0:30:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去艦隊會潰散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.21,0:30:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西雅哈絲，梅爾巴號的通訊\N還沒恢復嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.67,0:30:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能撤回艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.47,0:30:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前仍廼無法與梅爾巴通訊\N指揮系統陷入混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.59,0:30:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法再控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.85,0:30:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.89,0:30:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，派出全部的艦載機應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.31,0:30:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握制空權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.65,0:30:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.07,0:30:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在進入發艦準備\N副引擎準備點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.36,0:30:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副引擎點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.33,0:30:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除固定鎖\N拆除給油管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.79,0:30:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前進\N微風號脫離船塢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.18,0:31:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離完畢\N主引擎準備點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.85,0:31:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎開動\N發艦準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.39,0:31:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，請下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.48,0:31:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.24,0:31:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長，準備亞空間航行\N開始讀秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.87,0:31:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，開始讀秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.83,0:31:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始讀秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:28.33,0:31:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要出發了\N還是這個引擎聲音最好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.17,0:31:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲快開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.21,0:31:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍醫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.38,0:31:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.01,0:31:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有泰勒艦長跟特姆大人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.55,0:31:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.30,0:31:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上的重力\N對妳而言太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.60,0:31:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快上太空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.22,0:31:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.27,0:31:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.27,0:31:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.35,0:31:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.44,0:31:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.48,0:31:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.31,0:31:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.40,0:31:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.40,0:31:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.82,0:32:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微風號開始亞空間航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.02,0:32:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，新的艦隊接近過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:43.74,0:32:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到可見範圍後\N轉播到主螢幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.86,0:32:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.53,0:32:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開全部砲門\N採取攻擊陣形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.12,0:32:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.03,0:32:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，方向562\N看到敵人艦隊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.00,0:32:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在播到螢幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.33,0:33:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了，全體艦隊準備攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.55,0:33:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信士，通知全部艦艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.10,0:33:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入攻擊體勢\N陣形採鶴翼型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:15.64,0:33:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動部隊退後到艦隊的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.56,0:33:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海士，肥前號微速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.40,0:33:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他幹得挺像樣的\N中將大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.28,0:33:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦載機\N進入射程距離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.12,0:33:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到攻擊也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.99,0:33:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊的全部砲門\N對準敵人的旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.04,0:33:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦隊進入攻擊體勢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:43.88,0:33:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊目標集中本艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.88,0:33:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想來真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.76,0:33:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船長官\N已經完成攻擊體勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:52.89,0:33:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.82,0:34:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.78,0:34:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.40,0:34:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我發出最後通牒\N給敵人司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.32,0:34:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後通牒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.16,0:34:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電文就說我軍已因你們的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.54,0:34:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕貴國締結和平協定的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.75,0:34:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們為了和平投降?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.71,0:34:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，梅爾巴號的\N通訊命令中斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.05,0:34:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.35,0:34:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.02,0:34:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們，竟然背叛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:05.17,0:35:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們帝國被人侵略了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.26,0:35:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只知道發生強力的\N磁力線與紅色閃光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:14.10,0:35:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督… 陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.28,0:35:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人離開射程距離\N攻擊機散開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.41,0:35:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.54,0:35:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想投降嗎\N拉爾哥人會投降!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:41.66,0:35:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能\N難道他們真的想要和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.58,0:35:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.92,0:35:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是想要投降獲得和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.21,0:35:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要戰鬥到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.26,0:35:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信士，敵人解除戰鬥體勢了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.51,0:35:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼動靜也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.76,0:35:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.18,0:36:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雪舟三船\N只好見證到底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.28,0:36:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾哥不會投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.41,0:36:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要求和平的通訊也是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.20,0:36:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:23.00,0:36:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在將敵人逼入絕境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.54,0:36:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是敵人在將我們逼入絕境了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.84,0:36:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說八道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.97,0:36:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.01,0:36:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請任命我當艦隊司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.93,0:36:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N自不量力的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.89,0:36:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.65,0:36:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信的話\N是不會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.36,0:36:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋，你想汙辱邊境司令部的名聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.40,0:36:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態緊急呀，閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.07,0:37:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，我任命你當艦隊司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.00,0:37:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.37,0:37:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.03,0:37:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信士，傳電給所有艦艇\N維持戰鬥隊形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.92,0:37:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體機關部停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.67,0:37:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥前號微速前進\N開到敵人旗艦的正對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.47,0:37:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊了\N正向本艦正面靠近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.10,0:37:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，只有一艘旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.10,0:37:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艘?不管他們作戰計畫是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.10,0:37:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場仗絕不能投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.48,0:37:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦準備砲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:38.03,0:37:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，有艘船\N單獨從亞空間跳躍出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.29,0:37:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨?不要管小嘍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.85,0:37:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是敵人行星聯合宇宙軍旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:47.96,0:37:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備砲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.38,0:37:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是微風號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.67,0:37:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微風號!? 泰勒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.18,0:37:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.02,0:38:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.39,0:38:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.32,0:38:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源殘量0.8%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.98,0:38:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關部裝甲損壞嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.74,0:38:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎損傷\N微風號無法移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.78,0:38:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，到這裡就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.54,0:38:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長，幫我接上\N肥前號的三船艦隊司令長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.29,0:38:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.38,0:38:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艦隊司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.88,0:38:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.17,0:38:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀，那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.84,0:38:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請肥前號收容微風號全體船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.64,0:38:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.43,0:38:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香取中尉，金姆中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:47.10,0:38:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將各緊急艙門切換為手動操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.31,0:38:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.31,0:38:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.16,0:38:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請對艦橋的指揮官以外的船員\N發下退艦命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.32,0:38:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.78,0:38:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在騷動什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.40,0:38:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微風號的船員離艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:01.61,0:39:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻派救生艇前往收容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.83,0:39:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.33,0:39:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒想要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.33,0:39:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金姆中尉，打開對拉爾哥艦隊\N司令官的通信回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.17,0:39:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解，打開通信回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.92,0:39:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，收到微風號的通訊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.92,0:39:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，接上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.47,0:39:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是泰勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.22,0:39:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，特姆艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.76,0:39:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:28.93,0:39:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們拉爾哥帝國艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:31.73,0:39:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會為了表示追求和平的誠意\N在這場戰爭中投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.82,0:39:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降?是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.57,0:39:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降一點意義也沒有\N沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.33,0:39:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出現新的威脅的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.41,0:39:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵隊關係將會變得如何\N特姆艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.25,0:39:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人還是友軍呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.92,0:39:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒在講什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:56.71,0:39:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的敵人是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.30,0:40:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍遭到擁有強力磁力線武器\N放出紅色閃光的艦隊襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.55,0:40:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.26,0:40:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色閃光跟磁力線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.43,0:40:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟侵略梅爾巴號的情況一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.02,0:40:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾巴號?侵略?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.32,0:40:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿那張粗糙的照片幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.94,0:40:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我相信行星聯合宇宙軍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.03,0:40:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先要求我投降\N然後再來誑我!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.57,0:40:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆艦長，連照片上的事實\N你都不願相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.91,0:40:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎麼有辦法相信和平這東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.92,0:40:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有照片都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.26,0:40:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.76,0:40:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源殘量0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.72,0:40:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，微風號的機能都停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:50.72,0:40:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交給山本處理\N大家逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.48,0:40:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人，新的威脅難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.65,0:41:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是來告訴我這點的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.69,0:41:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱嗎，泰勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.32,0:41:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本艦長，泰勒艦長\N及其他七名官兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:07.03,0:41:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經搭乘最後的逃生小艇\N脫離微風號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.29,0:41:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點，快去收容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.31,0:41:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥前號打開所有砲門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:33.43,0:41:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是驅逐艦微風號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.48,0:41:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.52,0:41:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了嗎，山本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.82,0:41:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船中將閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.45,0:41:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微風號船員遵守軍規
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.95,0:41:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在邊境方面軍司令部的命令下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.47,0:41:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始為老朽艦艇微風號\N進行解體工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.74,0:41:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閣下批准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:01.09,0:42:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝泰勒艦長及驅逐艦微風號\N所有的船員的奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.72,0:42:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令批准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.39,0:42:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，謝謝閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.72,0:42:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部砲門打開，攻擊
